node.text: Selfie Susan forgot to check the tide report. #gottheshot #influencerslams

A live look at what happens when you open the doors at @crestliquorco @chipsliquor or @palmliquorpb. @kookslamshardseltzer is available throughout OC, LA and additional SD locations. Peep the store locator on our site to find where to get it or purchase online for CA delivery 🤙
